            Non-surgical and non-permanent</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="2c4b5654-c4ae-4c4d-9b8a-fe7b466580a6" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-01a676b9833b-26_"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-01a676b9833b-27_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-01a676b9833b-28_"><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-29_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-31_">Our product is not a hair transplant.&nbsp;</span></p><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-32_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-34_">It's a non invasive, non-surgical, semi-permanent solution.</span></p><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-35_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-37_">Using the product has no side effects and it can be removed when desired, leaving no scars or marks.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-01a676b9833b-38_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-01a676b9833b-39_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="a673fe2d-7118-49ed-995f-09c8ca999777" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>
            Preparing the head        </span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="a673fe2d-7118-49ed-995f-09c8ca999777" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-01a676b9833b-41_"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-01a676b9833b-42_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-01a676b9833b-43_"><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-44_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-46_">To use our product, the thinning/balding area on top of your head will have to be shaved. If your hair loss situation is partial and/or only located in the front (receding hairline) or only in the back (crown area), a surface size of minimum 4 inches square will need to be shaved to ensure solid and safe bonding of the hair system.</span></p><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-47_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-49_">If your hair loss situation is located in the front and in the back, with a good area of thick hair in between, the majority of the top of your head will still need to be shaved to cover the two balding zones with the hair piece and to obtain better and more realistic results.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-01a676b9833b-50_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-01a676b9833b-51_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="ca999777-b238-44e2-be99-610bdc75527f" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>
            Attachment to the head            </span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="ca999777-b238-44e2-be99-610bdc75527f" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-01a676b9833b-53_"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-01a676b9833b-54_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-01a676b9833b-55_"><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-56_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-58_">Our hair units can be attached to your scalp using special certified skin safe liquid adhesive or special double-sided tape. We offer these products in the maintenance products section of our shop.</span></p><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-59_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-61_">The attachment can be partial or full and can be done in different ways, offering bonds that will vary in resistance according to your needs and lifestyle.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-01a676b9833b-62_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-01a676b9833b-63_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="dc75527f-bbd8-45a7-9ba9-e1d138097504" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>
            Wear time    </span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="dc75527f-bbd8-45a7-9ba9-e1d138097504" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-01a676b9833b-65_"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-01a676b9833b-66_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-01a676b9833b-67_"><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-68_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-70_">You will wear the hair system between 2 to 4 weeks on your head, depending on your lifestyle, body chemistry and location’s weather conditions as well.</span></p><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-71_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-73_">Every 2 to 4 weeks, the hair system needs to be removed, the old adhesive will also need to be removed; the scalp will need to be cleaned and the hair that has regrown will need to be shaved again. The hair system will then be refitted to the scalp using fresh adhesive.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-01a676b9833b-74_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-01a676b9833b-75_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="38097504-2bc4-48d6-affa-dd509cc3be84" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>
            Made of real human hair</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="38097504-2bc4-48d6-affa-dd509cc3be84" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-01a676b9833b-77_"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-01a676b9833b-78_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-01a676b9833b-79_"><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-80_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-82_">All our hair systems are made with 100% natural human hair.</span></p><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-83_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-85_">Our premade units are made with A-grade virgin Indian hair and our custom units are made with superior authentic virgin Remy Indian hair.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-01a676b9833b-86_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-01a676b9833b-87_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="9cc3be84-1121-4207-8b11-93c3d6a11d71" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>Durability and lifespan</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="9cc3be84-1121-4207-8b11-93c3d6a11d71" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-01a676b9833b-89_"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-01a676b9833b-90_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-01a676b9833b-91_"><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-92_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-94_">The lifespan of our hair systems will depend on a variety of factors including the type of base material it is made of, the usage and the maintenance given to it.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-95_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-97_">Hair systems do naturally lose quality over time as the hair strands become more dry and worn looking. The frequency of the maintenance services (refits), the products used to style and maintain the hair, the exposure to the sun and the frequency of shampoos done to the hair are all factors that will make the hair strands age with time, the knots weaken and the base lose its shape and strength.</span></p><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-98_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-100_">Our hair systems are all designed to last between an average of 4 to 6 months, except our special ultra-thin skin hair system which has a lifespan of 2 to 3 months due to its extremely thin and fragile base material.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-01a676b9833b-101_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-01a676b9833b-102_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="71f4dedf-a742-41d0-b3b0-85ca00ed1cdc" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>Sweating / Showering / Wetting the hair</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="71f4dedf-a742-41d0-b3b0-85ca00ed1cdc" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-01a676b9833b-104_"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-01a676b9833b-105_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-01a676b9833b-106_"><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-107_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-109_">All our hair systems are designed to resist sweat and water exposure. What is affected by those elements is in fact the adhesive and not the hair unit itself.</span></p><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-110_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-112_">The adhesives we recommend are sweat and waterproof but they also each have limits to how much water/sweat exposure they can take before they start to break and need to be changed.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-01a676b9833b-113_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-01a676b9833b-114_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="00ed1cdc-999a-424e-a20c-6631eeb5ec94" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>
            Fitting and maintenance     </span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="00ed1cdc-999a-424e-a20c-6631eeb5ec94" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-01a676b9833b-116_"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-01a676b9833b-117_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-01a676b9833b-118_"><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-119_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-121_">OneHead is working hard everyday to offer fitting and maintenance services in as many cities worldwide as possible to accommodate all our new and existing customers.</span></p><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-122_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-124_">We have built an incredible team of affiliated and trained hair system stylists and this team is growing everyday to help more interested clients.</span></p><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-125_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-127_">We are proud to be able to offer fitting and maintenance services in major cities of the USA, Canada, UK, Europe, Middle-East, South Africa and Australia. See the Points of Service section under Contact Us for more details.</span></p><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-128_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-130_">If you don’t live nearby one of our certified hair stylist, don’t worry, many of our clients around the world are using our products without having one in their city.</span></p><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-131_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-133_">We have developed DIY guides and videos to allow you to use our product and maintain it by yourself, wherever you are located. We also offer special, hair dresser training sessions, via live video call.</span></p><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-134_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-136_">We encourage our new clients to either approach hair salons or hairdressers/barbers they might know (someone if their friends/family circle or a referral) in their city, explain they are looking for someone willing to learn the hair system fitting technique and help them with the product. We will assist and teach the stylist/barber for free, step by step, the fitting process of our product. We also have video tutorials for extra support.</span></p><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-137_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-139_">Get in touch with us to know more about these options.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-01a676b9833b-140_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-01a676b9833b-141_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="1ab975ff-5c4c-4a67-94eb-0eb4dc4d3696" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>
            Hair systems VS Hair transplants</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="1ab975ff-5c4c-4a67-94eb-0eb4dc4d3696" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-01a676b9833b-143_"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-01a676b9833b-144_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-01a676b9833b-145_"><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-146_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-148_">Many people are asking themselves this common question when looking for the perfect hair loss solution.</span></p><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-149_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-151_">They are actually two completely different solutions that will match different requirements on different people.</span></p><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-152_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-154_">Staying very transparent and honest, we have created a list of the pros and cons of each solution, to give you an overview of each, so you can better decide if one would be best for you.</span></p><div class="sc-lhMiDA hoDxgx pf-01a676b9833b-155_ pf-table-bordered pf-hide" data-pf-type="Table"><table><tbody><tr><th class="A1"><span>Hair Systems</span></th><th class="B1"><span>Hair Transplants</span></th></tr><tr><td class="A2"><span>Pros</span></td><td class="B2"><span>Pros</span></td></tr><tr><td class="A3"><span>• Non surgical or invasive<br>• Instant and guaranteed results<br>• Can be temporary<br>• Can be used at any age<br>• Fully customizable solution (hair density, color, style)<br></span></td><td class="B3"><span>• Ideal for light to medium hair loss situation<br>• Permanent solution<br>• Little maintenance required<br>• Cost per operation (vs recurring)<br></span></td></tr><tr><td class="A4"><span><span style="font-weight: bold;">Cons</span></span></td><td class="B4"><span><span style="font-weight: bold;">Cons</span></span></td></tr><tr><td class="A5"><span>• Medium to advance hair loss situations only
<br>• Regular maintenance needed<br>• Temporary solution
