<br>• 2 or 3 (or more) hair transplants normally needed to achieve</span></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-md:4;--c-lg:2"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-01a676b9833b-156_"></div></div></div><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-01a676b9833b-157_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-md:4;--c-lg:2"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-01a676b9833b-158_"></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-md:4;--c-lg:8"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-01a676b9833b-159_"><a data-pf-type="Button" class="sc-djWRfJ dtXvbo pf-01a676b9833b-160_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-162_">About Maintenance</span></a><div data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion" class="sc-cNKqjZ diijrs pf-01a676b9833b-163_"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-01a676b9833b-164_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-01a676b9833b-165_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="0fcb2389-e8a0-45eb-9cb1-860ed866ae95" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>
            How often do I need to do a maintenance of my system?      </span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="0fcb2389-e8a0-45eb-9cb1-860ed866ae95" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-01a676b9833b-167_"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-01a676b9833b-168_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-01a676b9833b-169_"><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-170_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-172_"><span style="font-weight: normal;">The average service/maintenance cycle is 2-4 weeks. Depending on your lifestyle and personal preferences, you may want to have a rebond maintenance service sooner than 2 weeks or later than 4 weeks however we do not recommend wearing your system more than 5-6 weeks without changing the adhesive.</span></span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-01a676b9833b-173_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-01a676b9833b-174_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="b1860ed8-66ae-453f-9d19-acbd7fa2280f" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>
            What's a maintenance session?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="b1860ed8-66ae-453f-9d19-acbd7fa2280f" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-01a676b9833b-176_"><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-01a676b9833b-177_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-01a676b9833b-178_"><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-179_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-181_"><span style="font-weight: normal;">A maintenance session consists in removing the hair system, cleaning and shampooing both your head and the system, shave the hair that has regrown under, then reapplying the system to your scalp using fresh adhesive.</span></span></p><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-182_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-184_"><span style="font-weight: normal;">If you are near one of our affiliated hairstylists, you can get your maintenance services with them. See the list of <a href="/pages/our-locations" target="_self">our locations</a> to see if there is one near you.</span></span></p><p class="sc-ehIJor eZpnKY pf-01a676b9833b-185_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-BHvUt fJlZte pf-01a676b9833b-187_"><span style="font-weight: normal;">Like most of our client do, you can also do your service/maintenance sessions by yourself using our instructional videos and we can also assist you with it via live video chat.</span></span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-md:4;--c-lg:2"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gXRojI kCnmwO pf-01a676b9833b-188_"></div></div></div><div class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-01a676b9833b-189_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs